    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Hey @jhiver, I agree with @Amxx it's arguably better to have `*` as long as it doesn't introduce an unexpected behavior, which I can't think of. Still, we'd like to consider this if there is a clear benefit of using it. Although [I see the Solidity thread](https://github.com/ethereum/solidity/issues/11882) doesn't recommend it, it's unclear why it'd be discouraged.\r\n\r\nDo you see any strong reason to remove it?",
