    "updated_at": "2023-06-07T21:52:56Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "As far as I know, this pattern is not discouraged. The comments in the Solidity issue don't give any explanation or further context. The issue is from 2021 and although it hasn't had activity it does seem that the team still wants to remove this syntax.\r\n\r\nI wouldn't be opposed to changing our code to remove this. However, this is a perfectly valid Solidity feature that Brownie should support... and it might be easier and faster for Brownie to fix this than it will be for us to create a release (something we avoid doing frequently).\r\n\r\n",
